+# CareOn — Phase 1 completion report (standardization phase)
+
+**Date:** 2026-06-18
+**Status:** **CLOSED — Complete.** This report formally closes the standardization phase (governance, verification, guardrails, and the additive M0 metric primitives).
+
+> All authoritative checks for PR-A–PR-D, the PR-C correction, and M0 were confirmed green by the repo owner. Evidence is recorded in §7. No verification remains open.
+>
+> **"Phase 1 Complete" refers to the actually approved and executed scope** (PR-A–PR-D + PR-C correction + M0). Two originally-listed Phase 1 items are formally **deferred**, not silently dropped (see §2a): **PR-E** (reliable Playwright smoke in CI) and **PR-F** (one official local/pre-PR verification command).
+
+---
+
