+- `contracts/views.py` decomposition ADR: `docs/adr/ADR-CONTRACTS-VIEWS-DECOMPOSITION.md`.
+- Standardization roadmap (3 workstreams) + Phase 1 implementation plan.
+- Primitives convergence decision with **D1–D4** formally recorded + 21-consumer heatmap: `CAREON_PRIMITIVES_CONVERGENCE_DECISION.md`.
+- Canonical document-hierarchy decision (see §4).
+
